! Local Setup Notes

Run from this directory:

```
npm start
```

Then open:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8081/
```

Build a standalone HTML export:

```
npm run build
```

The local Markdown wiki remains the durable canonical surface until an export
path is promoted.
